7 AS INTRODUCED
8 A Joint Resolution approving certain proposed
permanent rules of certain general government state
9 agencies; excluding certain Long-Range Capital
Planning Commission major rule changes; and directing
10 distribution.
11
12
13 WHEREAS, pursuant to Section 308 of Title 75 of the Oklahoma
14 Statutes, the Oklahoma State Legislature shall adopt a joint
15 resolution to approve or disapprove administrative rules.
16 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
17 AND THE SENATE OF THE 2ND SESSION OF THE 60TH OKLAHOMA LEGISLATURE:
18 SECTION 1. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
19 permanent rules of the Oklahoma Department of Aerospace and
20 Aeronautics filed on or before February 1, 2026.
21 SECTION 2. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
22 permanent rules of the Department of Consumer Credit filed on or
23 before February 1, 2026.
24
