1 SECTION 3. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
2 permanent rules of the Office of Management and Enterprise Services
3 filed on or before February 1, 2026.
4 SECTION 4. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
5 permanent rules of the Oklahoma Firefighters Pension and Retirement
6 System filed on or before February 1, 2026.
7 SECTION 5. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
8 permanent rules of the Long-Range Capital Planning Commission filed
9 on or before February 1, 2026, except for the following proposed
10 changes: OAC 428:15-1-1; 428:15-1-2; 428:15-1-3; 428:15-3-1; 428:15-
