13 SECTION 6. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
14 permanent rules of Service Oklahoma filed on or before February 1,
15 2026.
16 SECTION 7. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
17 permanent rules of the Department of Transportation filed on or
18 before February 1, 2026.
19 SECTION 8. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
20 permanent rules of the Oklahoma Department of Veterans Affairs filed
21 on or before February 1, 2026.
22 SECTION 9. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
23 permanent rules of the Oklahoma Department of Securities filed on or
24 before February 1, 2026.
